<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 rby ʿạlm ạnt bḍʿfy .. wạnt ạlhy ạlqwy ạlqdyr

[V2]
 wʿn shwạty btgẖfr tʿfy .. yạlly ʿndk rḥmẗ ktyr

[V3]
 ạ̹dyny rby mʿwnẗ wqwẗ .. ʿlsẖạn ạ̉shr wạ̉kwn ṣạḥy

[V4]
 wạ̉bqy̱ sẖhạdẗ brẗ wjwẗ .. wʿly̱ ạlswr mạsk bslạḥy

[V5]
 ṣḥyḥ ạlḥrb sẖdydẗ qwyẗ .. lkn nṣry hạykwn byk

[V6]
 tdyny gẖlbẗ ʿly̱ ạlkẖṭyẗ .. fạʿysẖ rạfʿ rạsy bạrḍyk

[V7]
 dy mnyẗ qlby ạ̉fwz brḍạk .. rby ạlgẖạly yạ ạḥly̱ nṣyb

[V8]
 wʿạysẖ shrạn mstny lqạk... wạtẖq ạnk jạy qryb</lyrics>
